### Using `xml-fmt` with pre-commit

Add it to your `.pre-commit-config.yaml`:

```yaml
- repo: https://github.com/tox-dev/xml-fmt
  rev: "" # Use the sha / tag you want to point at
  hooks:
    - id: pyproject-fmt
```
